snippet.title: Anti Duterte Ad by Trillanes

localized.description:
This is the controversial Anti Duterte ad that started airing in ABS-CBN. The other TV Networks have also taken part in the negative campaigning and started this ad and other negative anti-Duterte ads. It has also been reported that it has also started airing on radio stations nationwide..READ MORE: http://getitfromboy.blogspot.com/2016/05/anti-duterte-ads-starts-airing-on-abs.html

Pls. refrain from using foul languange in the comments section kasi di rin sya mapa-publish. Youtube has a profanity filter. So kung for example P.I. P.I. na lang isulat, wag yung buong salita. LOL..Thank you.
